OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FA record number of illegal e-bikes
OL,8,Fhave been seized over the last year
OL,9,Famid concerns they are a "death trap"
OL,10,Ffor pedestrians, as ITV News' Cari
OL,11,FDavies explains
OL,13,FPolice seizures of illegally modified
OL,14,Felectric bikes (e-bikes) soared in the
OL,15,Fpast year amid concerns their speed
OL,16,Fand weight present a lethal threat to
OL,17,Fpedestrians, an investigation has
OL,18,Ffound.
