OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FForces across the UK confiscated 937 e-
OL,8,Fbikes in the year to August 11,
OL,9,Faccording to Freedom of Information
OL,10,F(FoI) figures.
OL,12,FThat is compared with 511 during the
OL,13,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,15,FUnder UK law, e-bike motors must cut
OL,16,Fout when a speed of 15.5mph is
OL,17,Freached, but police are finding many
OL,18,Fhave been modified to be much faster.
