OL,7,FIt is also common for officers to find
OL,8,Fe-bikes that can be powered without
OL,9,Fthe pedals being turned, effectively
OL,10,Fmaking them electric mopeds or
OL,11,Fmotorbikes which must be registered
OL,12,Fand taxed.
OL,14,FConversion kits are available online
OL,15,Ffor as little as #300.
OL,17,FCity of London Police recently seized
OL,18,Fan e-bike capable of reaching 70mph,
OL,19,Fwhich featured an electronic display
OL,20,Findicating it had covered more than
OL,21,F6,000 miles.
