OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FDuring another operation outside
OL,8,FLondon Liverpool Street railway
OL,9,Fstation earlier this month, it took
OL,10,Fofficers just minutes to catch a rider
OL,11,Fusing an illegal e-bike.
OL,13,FThe e-bike had a motor with a maximum
OL,14,Fpower output was 500 watts - twice the
OL,15,Flegal limit -as well as severely worn
OL,16,Fout tyres and a bundle of loose
OL,17,Felectric wires stored in a soaking wet
OL,18,Fpouch.
