OL,7,FAn officer at the scene described it
OL,8,Fas "a death trap", adding: "This could
OL,9,Feasily kill him or someone else."
OL,11,FNo action was taken against the rider
OL,12,F- a food delivery worker - but his e-
OL,13,Fbike was confiscated and will likely
OL,14,Fbe destroyed.
OL,16,FTwenty-seven out of 46 police forces
OL,17,Fprovided data in response to PA's FoI
OL,18,Frequests.
