OL,3,CE-bike seizures surge as police find
OL,4,C'death trap' contraptions on the
OL,5,Cstreets
OL,7,FAmong the forces with the largest year-
OL,8,Fon-year increases in e-bike seizures
OL,9,Fwere Wiltshire Police (from 24 to 64),
OL,10,FPolice Scotland (from 60 to 233),
OL,11,FDerbyshire Police (from four to 23),
OL,12,FNorthumbria Police (from 18 to 58) and
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police (from 66 to 137).
OL,15,FSome forces said their figures related
OL,16,Fto all e-bike seizures, while others
OL,17,Fspecified their statistics were for
OL,18,Fillegal e-bikes.
