OL,7,FHe said: "The high speed and power of
OL,8,Fthese vehicles means they're ideal for
OL,9,Friders to come in, take the phone and
OL,10,Fget away before the victim knows
OL,11,Fwhat's happened."
OL,13,FThe speed and weight of illegally
OL,14,Fmodified e-bikes also "massively"
OL,15,Fheightens the danger for pedestrians
OL,16,Finvolved in collisions, Acting Sgt
OL,17,FHook said.
OL,19,F"The heaviest one I've seen was in
OL,20,Fexcess of 50kg. That bike (could reach
OL,21,Fover) 60mph.
