OL,7,F"If that impacts with somebody, it's
OL,8,Flikely to cause either serious injury
OL,9,For, God forbid, death."
OL,11,FActing Sgt Hook said people caught
OL,12,Friding an illegally adapted e-bikes
OL,13,Fcould face prosecution for a variety
OL,14,Fof offences such as not having
OL,15,Finsurance and number plates.
OL,17,FBut on most occasions, the only action
OL,18,Ftaken is to destroy their vehicle.
